eek the roots of video gaming fun. The team also includes Aline Krebs, young talented artist that led the art direction and Aymeric Schwartz, experienced composer and sound designer (Rayman Adventures, Absolver, Splasher…)  that provided BAFL with the perfect badass soundtrack to match the nervous gameplay.",
